title: Natural Food Store Farm
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located on the second floor of an organic health store is a cozy and inviting little lunch spot called The Farm. Serves two vegan lunch sets: Vegetable curry with brown rice and a small salad or vegetable deli sampler plate served with miso soup and brown rice. Home-style food of seasonal vegetables and a dessert (strawberry soy smoothie).  An English menu card is available.
